1 Задание:
Войдем в пользователя:
su - user1



2 Задание:

user1@eltex-practice2-v38:~$ ps -e -T | awk '{print $1}' | sort | uniq -c | awk '$1 > 1 {count++} END {print "Количество процессов с несколькими потоками:", count}'
Количество процессов с несколькими потоками: 10

3 Задание:

user1@eltex-practice2-v38:~$ top 

настраиваем таблицу в top:

Fields Management for window 1:Def, whose current sort field is %CPU
   Navigate with Up/Dn, Right selects for move then <Enter> or Left commits,
   'd' or <Space> toggles display, 's' sets sort.  Use 'q' or <Esc> to end!

* PID      = Process Id     SUPGRPS  = Supp Groups N  %CUU     = CPU Utilizati
* USER     = Effective Use  TGID     = Thread Group   %CUC     = Utilization +
* RUSER    = Real User Nam  OOMa     = OOMEM Adjustm  nsCGROUP = CGRP namespac
* PR       = Priority       OOMs     = OOMEM Score c  nsTIME   = TIME namespac
* NI       = Nice Value     ENVIRON  = Environment v
  VIRT     = Virtual Image  vMj      = Major Faults 
  RES      = Resident Size  vMn      = Minor Faults 
  SHR      = Shared Memory  USED     = Res+Swap Size


Вот так теперь выглядит таблица:
